# Keycloak Configuration for Nxr v2.0

## Realm: nxr

### Client: device-service

```json
{
  "clientId": "device-service",
  "enabled": true,
  "clientAuthenticatorType": "client-secret",
  "secret": "CHANGE_ME",
  "protocol": "openid-connect",
  "publicClient": false,
  "standardFlowEnabled": true,
  "directAccessGrantsEnabled": true,
  "serviceAccountsEnabled": true,
  "authorizationServicesEnabled": true,
  "redirectUris": [
    "http://localhost:8000/*",
    "https://api.nxr.io/*"
  ],
  "webOrigins": [
    "*"
  ],
  "attributes": {
    "access.token.lifespan": "3600",
    "client.secret.creation.time": "1234567890"
  }
}
```

### Client: api-gateway

```json
{
  "clientId": "api-gateway",
  "enabled": true,
  "clientAuthenticatorType": "client-secret",
  "secret": "CHANGE_ME",
  "protocol": "openid-connect",
  "publicClient": false,
  "standardFlowEnabled": true,
  "directAccessGrantsEnabled": true,
  "serviceAccountsEnabled": true,
  "authorizationServicesEnabled": true,
  "redirectUris": [
    "http://localhost:8000/*",
    "https://api.nxr.io/*"
  ],
  "webOrigins": [
    "*"
  ]
}
```

### Roles

- `admin`: Full access to all resources
- `device-manager`: Manage devices
- `device-viewer`: View devices only
- `plugin-manager`: Manage plugins
- `execution-manager`: Execute commands

### Identity Provider: Keystone (OpenStack)

```json
{
  "alias": "keystone",
  "providerId": "keycloak-oidc",
  "enabled": true,
  "config": {
    "clientId": "nxr-client",
    "clientSecret": "CHANGE_ME",
    "authorizationUrl": "https://keystone.example.com/v3/OS-FEDERATION/identity_providers/keystone/protocols/openid/authorize",
    "tokenUrl": "https://keystone.example.com/v3/OS-FEDERATION/identity_providers/keystone/protocols/openid/token",
    "userInfoUrl": "https://keystone.example.com/v3/auth/user",
    "jwksUrl": "https://keystone.example.com/v3/OS-FEDERATION/identity_providers/keystone/protocols/openid/.well-known/openid-configuration",
    "issuer": "https://keystone.example.com/v3"
  }
}
```

